5:
Excuse me, we'll take three whole
chickens, please!
9:
Getting stuff for the party is a lot
more work than I thought. I guess
we should've brought more people.
16:
I spy Voula! Whatcha doing? Going
somewhere?
19:
A-Arum! Uh... Nowhere special... Just
forget you saw me!
33:
Bad Voula! You know you're not
supposed to go in here alone.
Lightsy's gonna be so mad!
36:
I don't have a choice... If I want to
make it on my own... I need money...
39:
But Lightsy told me you moved to a
house with lots of other people in it.
42:
That place... isn't my home... And
neither is Palpebra! I just woke up in
this weird Kaleidoscope place one
day...
43:
I already have a home... I already
have parents!
45:
I'm not an orphan... I don't need
anyone's pity... or their help!
55:
Whatever, let's go. You wanna get
more elemental gems, right?
57:
You're still a big weakling, so I'll help
you, okay?
65:
Here I thought you were another
troublesome bunch of intruders... If it
isn't the cursed child and... some
other brat.
66:
I was planning to simply cast out
any adventurers I happened across,
but you... I can use you...
69: Whoa! You scared me! Who are you?
73:
I am but the unlucky soul always
relegated to cleaning up someone's
mess.
O all-devouring Darkness, heed my
call—
78:
Ahaha! Does that mean it's okay for
me to beat you up? Here we go!
86:
Hahaha... You're rather good. Yes...
You'll prove quite useful!
95:
It seems you're not very clever,
though...
101: Huh?! I can't move... You... You...
104:
Break us out of here, Shadow
Chariot!
109:
A-Arum, I'm sorry! This is all my
fault... You followed me in here...
112:
Why are you apologizing? The bad
guy is that weird old man.
116:
And it's okay! I know exactly what to
do!
118:
When you're in trouble, everyone
told me to do this...
122: Help! Nimbus, Alk, Lightsy, SAVE ME!
137: See? It's just like Lightsy said!
140:
It's okay to ask for help! They'll
always be here to lend a hand!
144:
Tch... It's that meddlesome sword
again...
151:
Arum, what were you thinking! I
thought we told you not to go into
the Kaleidoscope alone!
155:
But I wasn't alone... I had Voula with
me...
160:
I don't want to hear any excuses! No
candy for the rest of the year!
174:
We won't always make it in time to
save you, understand? Don't... Don't
be so reckless, okay?
182:
Voula! Oh, thank goodness you're
safe!
189:
Do you think our mama's... as
worried as that person was?
201:
U-um, Arum, the orphanage director
just told me something...
203:
There's gonna be a holiday party
tomorrow at the orphanage, but...
204:
I... I don't know anybody there... She
said I can invite a friend if I want...
210:
A fine proposition. I say you go and
have a good time.
218: I'll go! I'll definitely be there!
